  "synopsis": "Tong Qi, a girl who was instilled with otaku culture by her parents since childhood but tried her best not to be associated with \"otaku,\" always regarded her deskmate, Yang Wei, a pure and sunny boy in the real world, as her idol. Unexpectedly, one day, she heard the word \"anime/manga\" from this \"idol\"... The hilarious life of a big-handed mother and a naive boy, otaku parents and a daughter who is good at complaining, is about to unfold!\n\n(Source: Bilibili, translated)",
